      <title>hexo踩坑</title>
      <link href="/2020/05/21/hexo-cai-keng/"/>
      <url>/2020/05/21/hexo-cai-keng/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="0x00前言"><a href="#0x00前言" class="headerlink" title="0x00前言"></a>0x00前言</h2><p>部署在腾讯云上都博客被我手贱重装了服务器，博客数据也全部没了。</p><p>所以我打算使用hexo来搭建博客，实惠不用付出一笔服务器的开支。</p><p>而且静态的博客访问速度快还很安全不用担心服务器被攻击等问题</p><h2 id="0x01准备工作"><a href="#0x01准备工作" class="headerlink" title="0x01准备工作"></a>0x01准备工作</h2><h6 id="环境："><a href="#环境：" class="headerlink" title="环境："></a>环境：</h6><p>Windows 10 1909</p><h6 id="必须品："><a href="#必须品：" class="headerlink" title="必须品："></a><strong>必须品：</strong></h6><p><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>账号一个</p><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git-2.26.2-64-bit</a></p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v12.16.3/node-v12.16.3-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">node-v12.16.3-x64</a></p><h6 id="创建一个文件夹保存博客文件"><a href="#创建一个文件夹保存博客文件" class="headerlink" title="创建一个文件夹保存博客文件"></a><strong>创建一个文件夹保存博客文件</strong></h6><h6 id="使用node安装hexo"><a href="#使用node安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="使用node安装hexo"></a><strong>使用node安装hexo</strong></h6><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">$ <span class="token function">npm</span> i -g hexo$ hexo init</code></pre><h2 id="0x02生成SSH钥"><a href="#0x02生成SSH钥" class="headerlink" title="0x02生成SSH钥"></a>0x02生成SSH钥</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">$ <span class="token function">git</span> config --global user.name <span class="token string">"John Doe"</span>$ <span class="token function">git</span> config --global user.email johndoe@example.com$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="token string">'上面的邮箱'</span>$ <span class="token function">ssh</span> -T git@github.com</code></pre><p>Windows 默认保存在 C:\Users\user\.ssh 下</p><h2 id="0x03添加密钥创建博客库"><a href="#0x03添加密钥创建博客库" class="headerlink" title="0x03添加密钥创建博客库"></a>0x03添加密钥创建博客库</h2><p><img src="/.io//C:%5CUsers%5CWo_x0rz4%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20200522091523809.png" alt="image-20200522091523809"></p><p><img src="/.io//C:%5CUsers%5CWo_x0rz4%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20200522091546313.png" alt="image-20200522091546313"></p><p><img src="/.io//C:%5CUsers%5CWo_x0rz4%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20200522091557787.png" alt="image-20200522091557787"></p><h2 id="0x04创建一篇文章并生成以及部署"><a href="#0x04创建一篇文章并生成以及部署" class="headerlink" title="0x04创建一篇文章并生成以及部署"></a>0x04创建一篇文章并生成以及部署</h2><p>最后执行以下命令就可以部署上传啦，以下 g 是 generate 缩写，d 是 deploy 缩写：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save hexo-deployer-git$ hexo new <span class="token string">'文章标题'</span>$ hexo g -d</code></pre><p>参考</p><p><a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000017986794" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000017986794</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
